Differentially expressed miRNAs were identified using the TPM and IDEG6 [62] software. TPM (Tags Per Million reads) is a standardized method for calculating miRNA expression levels. TPM values were calculated using the following equation:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
